{"tid":1017472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天盛苑女子趁家人熟睡 　攀窗墮樓命殞","createTime":"2019-02-11T12:49:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T12:56:07.000Z","uid":160807,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9b9eb026d75e7db0e08a16e6069bf86f5aefedeb","tid":1017472,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T12:49:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190210/photo/bkn-20190210031008890-0210_00822_001_01b.jpg?20190210154220\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190210%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190210031008890-0210_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20190210154220&h=285d7e3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天水圍天盛苑發生墮樓事件，今日(10日)凌晨2時半，一名姓何(55歲)女子於盛頤閣高處墮下，倒臥平台毫無反應，消防員及救護員到場將她抬返地面，可惜證實已死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警員調查後，聯絡到事主家人，證實她是大廈住客，有情緒病紀錄，懷疑趁家人熟睡，由廚房攀窗墮下，正調查她尋死原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190210/bkn-20190210031008890-0210_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190210%2Fbkn-20190210031008890-0210_00822_001.html&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu1yvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=c0e0e3ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190210/bkn-20190210031008890-0210_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"75c0bbddd2d3a7f6c7040871d6f50a0a4baf4763","tid":1017472,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T12:56:07.000Z","msg":"奶波魔魔召喚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fa